{"tid":1435494,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《荃灣斬人》北角重組左啦，知道狗狗又講大話。咁荃灣呢？傷者俾人斬到見骨呀！！","createTime":"2019-08-09T05:20:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T08:15:46.000Z","uid":278443,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"32e58a9f6f01e58bfbefb6b5c847480a3f7fef46","tid":1435494,"uid":278443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T05:20:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9FYYZvS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9FYYZvS.png&h=64cc9283&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/moRPmKd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmoRPmKd.png&h=be06e933&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家係米唔記得晒<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>荃灣斬人</strong></span></span>呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有人俾人斬到重傷架，點解可以無人提架！一個人都捉唔到呀！！！<br />\n立場記者觀察，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>警犬去到現場係無拉到任何人架，無做任何調查呀</strong></span></span>，淨係黎驅趕示威者。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家快D幫手重組埋荃灣斬人事件啦，有片出片有相出相，推到俾傳媒幫手重組埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n煮重佢米啦大佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: green;\">警黑勾結已經第三單啦！！！<br />\n元朗<br />\n北角<br />\n荃灣</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LoqgMgi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLoqgMgi.jpg&h=4d9348a2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8080c5c1316